          "c3": "Ish gay-eh tsoom Shal-ter, vile ish hil-feh brow-khe"
        },
        {
          "c1": "Do you have my passport and my visa?",
          "c2": "Haben Sie meinen Pass und mein Visum?",
          "c3": "Ha-ben zee mine-en Pass oond mine Vee-zoom?"
        },
        {
          "c1": "Watch out! My suitcase is very big.",
          "c2": "Vorsicht! Mein Koffer ist sehr groß",
